    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Yes, there are plenty of free audio players on Windows. There are also many free audio players on linux - however, I will prefer Amarok every time on every system I use. This Gollum-like obsession and jealousy between operating systems doesn't help anyone.</p>
